---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Asset Management — Onchain Yield">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Asset Management</span><span class="lang-zh">資產管理</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">How Funds Access<br/>Onchain Yield</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">基金如何獲取<br/>鏈上收益</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">BlackRock's BUIDL has $2.4B in tokenized Treasuries. Franklin Templeton's BENJI manages $742M. These are not crypto-native experiments — they're asset management products from the world's largest fund managers, built onchain.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">BlackRock嘅BUIDL持有$2.4B代幣化美債。Franklin Templeton嘅BENJI管理$742M。呢啲唔係crypto原生實驗 — 係全球最大基金管理公司嘅資產管理產品，建立在鏈上。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Products -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Tokenized Treasury Products</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化美債產品</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">BlackRock BUIDL</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">$2.4B AUM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">What:</span> Tokenized US Treasury fund — each BUIDL token represents a share in a fund holding short-term US government securities. Yield accrues daily.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">內容：</span>代幣化美債基金 — 每個BUIDL代幣代表持有短期美國國債基金的份額。收益每日累計。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Chains:</span> Available on 9 blockchains including Ethereum, Solana, and Avalanche.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">支援區塊鏈：</span>在9條區塊鏈上可用，包括Ethereum、Solana和Avalanche。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Use as collateral:</span> Binance accepts BUIDL as trading collateral — a powerful signal for institutional adoption. DeFi protocols are also integrating BUIDL as collateral.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">用作抵押品：</span>Binance接受BUIDL作為交易抵押品 — 機構採用的強力信號。DeFi協議亦正整合BUIDL作為抵押品。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Franklin Templeton BENJI</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">$742M AUM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">What:</span> OnChain US Government Money Fund (FOBXX) — the first US-registered fund to use a public blockchain for transaction processing and share ownership recording.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">內容：</span>OnChain US Government Money Fund (FOBXX) — 首隻使用公共區塊鏈進行交易處理和股份所有權記錄的美國註冊基金。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Chains:</span> Stellar and Polygon.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">支援區塊鏈：</span>Stellar和Polygon。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en"><span class="text-white font-medium">Significance:</span> Proves that a $1.5T+ AUM fund manager can operate onchain within existing regulatory frameworks.</span><span class="lang-zh"><span class="text-white font-medium">意義：</span>證明管理超$1.5T資產的基金管理公司可在現有監管框架內在鏈上運營。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Onchain -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Why Put Treasuries Onchain</span><span class="lang-zh">為什麼將美債上鏈</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Composability</span><span class="lang-zh">可組合性</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Tokenized treasuries can be used as collateral across DeFi protocols, margin accounts, and structured products. One asset, multiple uses — simultaneously earning yield while serving as collateral.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">代幣化美債可在DeFi協議、保證金賬戶和結構化產品中用作抵押品。一種資產，多重用途 — 同時賺取收益並用作抵押品。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">24/7</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">No custody transfer delays. No settlement windows. Subscriptions and redemptions happen in minutes, not days. Asian investors don't need to wait for US market hours.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">無託管轉移延遲。無結算窗口。認購和贖回在數分鐘內完成，而非數天。亞洲投資者無需等待美國市場時段。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Transparency</span><span class="lang-zh">透明度</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Holdings are verifiable onchain. NAV is real-time, not end-of-day. Audit trail is immutable. This is a higher standard of transparency than traditional fund structures.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">持倉可在鏈上驗證。資產淨值實時更新，而非日終。審計記錄不可篡改。這是比傳統基金結構更高的透明度標準。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Onchain Yield Strategies -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Onchain Yield Strategies for Funds</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">基金的鏈上收益策略</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">1. Tokenized Treasuries (Lowest Risk)</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">1. 代幣化美債（最低風險）</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Hold BUIDL, BENJI, or similar products for US Treasury yields onchain. Same underlying as a traditional money market fund. Risk profile: US government credit risk + smart contract risk.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">持有BUIDL、BENJI或類似產品以獲取鏈上美債收益。底層資產與傳統貨幣市場基金相同。風險概況：美國政府信用風險 + 智能合約風險。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">2. Stablecoin Lending (Low–Medium Risk)</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">2. 穩定幣借貸（低至中等風險）</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Supply USDC to institutional-grade lending protocols (Aave, Morpho, Compound). Yields typically 3–8% depending on market conditions. Risk: smart contract risk + borrower liquidation risk, mitigated by over-collateralization.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">向機構級借貸協議（Aave、Morpho、Compound）提供USDC。收益率通常3-8%，視市場狀況而定。風險：智能合約風險 + 借款人清算風險，通過超額抵押緩解。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">3. Stablecoin LP (Medium Risk)</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">3. 穩定幣流動性提供（中等風險）</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Provide liquidity to USDC/USDT AMM pools. Low impermanent loss for correlated pairs. Yields from trading fees. Used by more sophisticated funds comfortable with smart contract risk.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">向USDC/USDT AMM池提供流動性。相關資產對的無常損失低。收益來自交易費用。適合對智能合約風險有認知的成熟基金。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">4. ETH Staking (Medium Risk)</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">4. ETH質押（中等風險）</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Stake ETH to earn network rewards (~3-4% APR). Liquid staking tokens (stETH, rETH) allow continued use of capital while staking. SFC has approved staking for licensed VATPs in HK.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">質押ETH以賺取網絡獎勵（約3-4% APR）。流動質押代幣（stETH、rETH）允許在質押同時繼續使用資金。SFC已批准香港持牌VATP提供質押服務。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HK Context -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Context</span><span class="lang-zh">香港背景</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en">Hong Kong's regulatory environment increasingly supports institutional onchain yield. Key enablers:</span><span class="lang-zh">香港的監管環境越來越支持機構級鏈上收益。關鍵推動因素：</span></p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4">
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Licensed VATPs</span><span class="lang-zh">持牌VATP</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">12 licensed platforms provide regulated on/off ramps for institutional capital</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">12間持牌平台為機構資金提供受監管的出入金通道</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Staking Approved</span><span class="lang-zh">質押已獲批</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">SFC greenlit staking for licensed platforms (April 2025) — regulated crypto yield is now real</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">SFC批准持牌平台提供質押服務（2025年4月）— 受監管的加密收益已成現實</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Family Office Tax</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室稅務</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">Digital assets qualify for profit tax exemption under the family office regime (Feb 2026)</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">數字資產在家族辦公室制度下可享利得稅豁免（2026年2月）</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-800/30 rounded-lg p-4">
            <p class="text-white text-sm font-medium mb-1">
              <span class="lang-en">Banking Support</span><span class="lang-zh">銀行支持</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
              <span class="lang-en">Standard Chartered offers spot crypto trading. HSBC runs tokenized deposits. The banking layer is ready.</span>
              <span class="lang-zh">渣打提供現貨加密交易。HSBC運營代幣化存款。銀行基礎設施已就緒。</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Exploring onchain yield for your fund?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">為你的基金探索鏈上收益？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We can walk through the options and risk profiles relevant to your mandate.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們可以詳細討論與你的投資授權相關的選項和風險概況。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-between">
      <a href={`${base}/apply/investment-banking`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">← Investment Banking</span><span class="lang-zh">← 投資銀行</span>
      </a>
      <a href={`${base}/apply/family-offices`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">Family Offices →</span><span class="lang-zh">家族辦公室 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
